description:
Published article in LWT describing the optimization of microwave-assisted extraction (MAE) conditions for recovering bioactive compounds from oregano and lovage using ethanolic solvents. The work evaluates key extraction parameters to improve yield and efficiency, with the aim of enhancing the recovery of phenolic and other bioactive constituents from plant matrices. The findings contribute to the development of more efficient and sustainable extraction techniques for the valorisation of aromatic and medicinal plants.   
  &nbsp;  
